{
  "name": "NavGPT-CE",
  "description": "NavGPT reasoning graph for continuous VLN-CE — panoramic 8-direction perception with VLM captioning, plan decomposition, observation summarizer, orchestrator reasoning, and LLM-based history update. Faithful adaptation of NavGPT (Zhou et al., 2023) discrete panoramic pipeline to continuous environments.",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "episode_info",
      "type": "env_habitat__reset",
      "label": "Habitat: Episode Info",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 830
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "skill_action_format",
      "type": "navgpt__action_output_format",
      "label": "Skill: Action Format",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 320
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "seed_panorama",
      "type": "env_habitat__observe_panorama",
      "label": "Habitat: Panorama (seed)",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 120
      },
      "config": {
        "n_views": 12,
        "representation": "composite"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "seed_localize",
      "type": "env_habitat__observe_egocentric",
      "label": "Habitat: Localize",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "iter_in",
      "type": "iterIn",
      "label": "Iteration Gate",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 600
      },
      "config": {
        "version": 3,
        "pairedWith": "iter_out",
        "initPorts": [
          {
            "name": "rgb",
            "wire_type": "IMAGE",
            "persist": true
          },
          {
            "name": "pose",
            "wire_type": "POSE",
            "persist": true
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "vlm_caption",
      "type": "llmCall",
      "label": "VLM Panorama Caption",
      "position": {
        "x": 280,
        "y": 600
      },
      "config": {
        "temperature": 0.2,
        "max_tokens": 1024,
        "template": "You are looking at a panoramic composite of views from an indoor location, arranged in a grid. Each sub-image is labeled with its direction or heading angle at the top.\n\nFor each labeled view, describe what you see in 1-2 sentences. Focus on: room type, key objects and landmarks (furniture, doors, corridors, stairs), spatial layout, doorways, and any visible text or signs. Be factual and concise.\n\nFormat your response as:\n<direction_label>: <description>\n<direction_label>: <description>\n...\n\nCover every labeled view in the composite image."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "obs_summary_llm",
      "type": "llmCall",
      "label": "Obs Summary LLM",
      "position": {
        "x": 560,
        "y": 600
      },
      "config": {
        "temperature": 0.0,
        "max_tokens": 100,
        "mode": "single_turn",
        "template": "Here is a panoramic scene description from 8 directions at the current viewpoint:\n{scene}\n\nSummarize the overall scene in one concise sentence, highlighting the most navigation-relevant features (doorways, corridors, room type):"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "format_history",
      "type": "navgpt__format_history",
      "label": "Format History",
      "position": {
        "x": 280,
        "y": 440
      },
      "config": {
        "max_entries": 20
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "orchestrator_llm",
      "type": "llmCall",
      "label": "Orchestrator LLM",
      "position": {
        "x": 840,
        "y": 600
      },
      "config": {
        "ports": [
          {
            "name": "scene",
            "wire_type": "TEXT"
          },
          {
            "name": "summary",
            "wire_type": "TEXT"
          },
          {
            "name": "pose",
            "wire_type": "POSE"
          },
          {
            "name": "instruction",
            "wire_type": "TEXT"
          },
          {
            "name": "system_prompt",
            "wire_type": "TEXT"
          }
        ],
        "temperature": 0.0,
        "max_tokens": 300,
        "mode": "single_turn",
        "template": "You are an intelligent embodied agent navigating an indoor environment. You follow a plan derived from a natural language instruction by observing a 360° panorama and choosing discrete actions at each step.\n\nAvailable actions:\n- FORWARD  — move 0.25 m ahead in your current heading direction\n- LEFT     — turn left 15°\n- RIGHT    — turn right 15°\n- STOP     — you have reached the destination\n\nAction plan:\n{plan}\n\nHistory (recent steps):\n{history}\n\n360° panoramic observation (multiple directions from current viewpoint):\n{scene}\n\nScene summary: {summary}\n\nCurrent position: {pos}, heading {heading}° (0°=North, 90°=East, 180°=South, 270°=West)\nYour current heading is the 'Front' or '0°' direction in the panorama.\n\nInstruction: {instruction}\n\nStep: {step}\n\nBased on the action plan, history, and what you see in ALL directions of the panorama, decide your next action.\n- Compare what is visible in each direction with what the plan expects you to see next.\n- To face a direction that is currently to your right, use RIGHT repeatedly (each turn is 15°).\n- To face a direction that is currently to your left, use LEFT repeatedly.\n- Avoid revisiting places you have already been (check the history).\n- If the destination is visible and you are close, use STOP.\n\nOutput exactly in this format:\nThought: <brief reasoning about which direction matches the plan>\nAction: <FORWARD|LEFT|RIGHT|STOP>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "parse_action",
      "type": "navgpt__parse_action",
      "label": "Parse Action",
      "position": {
        "x": 1120,
        "y": 600
      },
      "config": {}
    },
